{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM09_ED2_030.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x3e,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Visitors from a far away country.<CR>Their interaction with Ayesha began<CR>with the most minor of events."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "The two had an interesting relationship,<CR>and before she knew it, Ayesha found<CR>herself deeply intrigued by it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "However, these visitors eventually had<CR>to leave. As they departed, Marion and<CR>Linca posed an unexpected proposition."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, thank you for everything. I was finally able to accomplish my mission..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "And it's all thanks to your help.<CR>Thank you so much for all you've<CR>done up till now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "So you have to go home... Thinking about how you two will be gone..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Makes me so sad..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Don't make that face.<CR>Being sad...it's the same for us, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "In a land where we've never been before, meeting and interacting with people we've never met before..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "We were able to make a smooth transition into this life right away thanks to you, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Because of you, we did not miss a meal. It is all thanks to you, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Okay... *sniff* Umm, will I ever see you two again?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Of course! ...Is what I'd like to say, but the truth is, I'm not sure."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It all depends on the higher-ups whether or not we'll be included in the next expedition team to be dispatched..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, being a gofer is hard..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "This place is too far for me to visit on my time off..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What...? Then I really might never see you two again...? *sniff*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "About that, Ayesha...Marion has something to talk to you about."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "*sniff* *sniff* ...Huh? Something to talk to me about?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. I was debating about whether or not to tell you this, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "We don't want this to be our good-bye to you, either."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "But we don't want to pressure you.<CR>We want you to think about it for<CR>yourself and reach your own decision."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "O-Okay... What is it...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "We'll be returning to the center. It's not the same as here, but it's not a bad place."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "To our land...would you like to...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Would you like to come with us, Ayesha!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Wha‐me...? To your town...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Rather than a town, it's run like a nation."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Our nation provides courteous aid to alchemists. We have several alchemists like you, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I really want you to think about it. It's a decision that'll greatly change your life."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "But if you feel like you want to come with us..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "We'll help you once we get there, just like how you helped us."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Right, Linca?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Of course. Ayesha is our companion,<CR>our buddy, our pal."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Marion, Linca...thank you so much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "...That was such a touching story.<CR>So how did we end up like this?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sorry about that. I didn't think we'd get transfer orders on the boat ride home."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "That was totally unexpected... *sigh*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Marion...it is hot. Requesting permission to cut my hair."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "No, absolutely not!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Then, requesting permission to take off my clothes..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What!? That's an absolutely not, too!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Besides, it gets drastically cold at night. So just wait till then."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Boo..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "*hah* *hah* Oh, Marion! There's water over there!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2e,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "*huff* *huff* C-Cold water!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2f,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Huh? I can assure you, there isn't any water around here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x30,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It's just a mirage.<CR>Don't bother running after it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x31,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What's a mirage...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x32,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "An illusion that makes you see water on a hot day."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x33,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "You'll have to wait till we return to the center to get cold water."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x34,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "And when will that be...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x35,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Who knows? It might be three full cycles of seasons."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x36,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What!? You mean three years!?<CR>That can't be..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x37,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "This is all because Marion is a gofer..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x38,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What did you say!? It's not like I asked to be transferred!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x39,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ugh, fine then! I've come this far,<CR>so let's finish this!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, what Marion is trying to say is that life is full of uncertainties that point to a dark future."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Gaaahhh. But being dark might cool things down..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hey, you there, cut the chatter. You're just gonna make your throat dry out."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Now, ancient ruin that sleeps in the desert sands, just you wait!"
        }
    ]
}